(42, 3, 13, 49, 4, 28, 28, 'Exact no more than that which is appointed you', 'Theft and Fair Labor', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of ethical behavior in work and financial dealings. Luke 3:13 advises against taking more than what is due, while Ephesians 4:28 encourages honest labor to support others.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
